description: Akwaaba Mining Ltd. engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral properties in Ghana, Africa. The company primarily explores for gold deposits. It owns interest in the Kunsu project located in the Ahafo Ano South District of the Ashanti Region of Ghana. The company was formerly known as Castle Peak Mining Ltd. and changed its name to Akwaaba Mining Ltd. in February 2022. Akwaaba Mining Ltd. was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Port Coquitlam, Canada.
